Fenerbahce congress member Murat Zorlu claims Fenerbahce are very close to completing a deal for Arsenal&rsquo;s Mesut Ozil ahead of the January transfer window.<br />
<br />
Zorlu has informed Sport Digitale the Turkish side are now looking to get the player in the new year: &ldquo;A source, who&rsquo;s very well connected to the club has told me that Mesut Ozil is likely to become a Fenerbahce player during the next transfer window. I would say 90% he will join us in one month.&rdquo;
